#

Nutella and Strawberry Toast

5 min
$2.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

GlutenDairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Course:

Tags:

Description

A quick and indulgent treat, perfect for breakfast or a sweet snack!

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • nutella: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh strawberries: 5-6, sliced
  • honey (optional): 1 teaspoon
